2. Tap the "+" icon to create a new reminder.

4. Set the time to 5:00 pm.
5. Tap "Save" to confirm.

*For Desktop:*

1. Open your digital calendar (e.g., Google Calendar, Apple Calendar).
2. Create a new event.
3. Set the title to "Reminder at 5 pm" (or your desired text).
4. Set the time to 5:00 pm.
5. Click "Save" to confirm.
